    Space Physics Archive Search and Extract (SPASE). The outermost container or envelope for SPASE metadata. This indicates the start of the SPASE metadata.

      • getCatalogOrDisplayDataOrNumericalData

        public java.util.List<java.lang.Object> getCatalogOrDisplayDataOrNumericalData()
        Gets the value of the catalogOrDisplayDataOrNumericalData property.

        This accessor method returns a reference to the live list, not a snapshot. Therefore any modification you make to the returned list will be present inside the JAXB object. This is why there is not a set method for the catalogOrDisplayDataOrNumericalData property.

        For example, to add a new item, do as follows: 

            getCatalogOrDisplayDataOrNumericalData().add(newItem);

        Objects of the following type(s) are allowed in the list Catalog DisplayData NumericalData Document Granule Instrument Observatory Person Registry Repository Service Annotation
